reviewText: Movie is so funny. If your in to STUPID-FUNNY...
Love this series, very obscure and hard to find. Love that it has english and japanese options. Watch the japanese first.
This is my favorite anime series EVER. The dvd case came on time. It was still factory sealed and had the insert inside yet. I've never been so excited!
It came in great condition and got it quick. I enjoyed watching the anime enough to get all the volumes.
